name: F U Rock N Roll Portraits

metadata.name: F U Rock N Roll Portraits #1
metadata.description: Neil Zlozower is one of rock’s most renowned photographers, having captured iconic images for Van Halen, Motley Crue, Guns N Roses, The Who, Kiss, Rolling Stones, Tom Petty, David Bowie, Led Zeppelin and thousands more. Neil’s documentary film “In Your Face”, tells the story of how Zloz, as he’s affectionately called, soared through the ranks of rock royalty during the 70’s, 80’s, 90’s and 2000’s! Zloz’s credits include more than 800 worldwide magazine covers, numerous album covers for the most celebrated artists, and photo shoots of virtually every major rock artist over the past 50 years.
